divs: Sighting DetailsI woke up at 546am this morning, I felt compelled to grab my binoculars and look at stars. In the northwest sky I spotted a ultra white orb that flew in a southeast direct. Watched it for about 3 minutes until it was gone. My heart is racing damn that was freaky.
